    "We only included articles that met all inclusion criteria.",
    "The selection process of the included articlesThe PRISMA flowchart shown in Fig. 1 outlines the process for selecting the articles we included in the review [26].",
    "The screening process began with the removal of duplicates, followed by a systematic review of titles, abstracts, and full texts against the inclusion criteria outlined in Table 2.",
